程序包 uestc.zhanghanwen.ATTCK.Wrappers

类 ResponseWrapper

java.lang.Object
uestc.zhanghanwen.ATTCK.Wrappers.ResponseWrapper
public class ResponseWrapper extends Object
The HTTP response should be sent to the client.
The object can be serialized into JSON string via toString()
版本:
1.0
作者:
zhanghanwen
